Optimize Data Extraction by Excluding Rows in Tabular Data

Exclude rows during tabular data extraction that you do not need to save by using the new Skip record option in the Intelligent Document Reader. Gain better control over the extraction process to capture only the relevant information.

Where: This change applies to the Lightning Experience of multiple Industries clouds.

Who: Apart from Financial Services Cloud, Health Cloud, and Public Sector Solutions, Intelligent Document Reader is also available with the Intelligent Document Reader add-on license for the Automotive, Consumer Goods, Education, Manufacturing, Media, and Net Zero clouds.
title: Optimize Data Extraction in Tabular Data
